00:21:42.217 --> 00:21:48.489
ober zey zenen zenen geven di eltern, ober di kinder zenen geboyrn gevorn shoyn dernokhn a- ale in Varshe.

00:21:49.592 --> 00:21:52.407
iz er hot zikh gelernt aleyn tsushnaydn,

00:21:52.407 --> 00:21:56.268
un ven er hot gemoldn dem tatn zaynem, a kotsker khosid,

00:21:56.578 --> 00:22:01.061
in di yeshi- yeshive er hot gelernt iz oykh geven fun kotsker rebn,

00:22:01.303 --> 00:22:03.069
iz hot er

00:22:03.733 --> 00:22:07.856
hot hot er gezogt az er f- er sh- er tsit zikh arayn keyn Varshe,

00:22:07.884 --> 00:22:10.075
vayl er geyt arop fun di kest,

00:22:10.095 --> 00:22:13.464
un er muz zukhn parnose far di oy- far di familye.

00:22:13.605 --> 00:22:16.856
hot men zikh gezetst shive. veyst vos heyst shive zitsn?

00:22:17.250 --> 00:22:18.487
nokh an UNK,

00:22:18.532 --> 00:22:20.028
un geshnitn krie.

00:22:20.844 --> 00:22:22.385
sh- me shnaydt arayn.

00:22:20.921 --> 00:22:22.120
vayl er iz ge⟨UNK⟩,

00:22:22.385 --> 00:22:24.281
vayl er iz gevorn a balmelokhe.

00:22:24.354 --> 00:22:26.559
a tsushnayder fun mener,

00:22:27.273 --> 00:22:30.355
fun mener p- mantlen un antsiger.

00:22:30.564 --> 00:22:33.025
bloyz far mener hot er zikh gelernt

00:22:33.028 --> 00:22:35.143
fun zikh aleyn, tsu shnaydn

00:22:35.143 --> 00:22:38.945
un er iz geven der ongezeenster tsushnayder in Varshe.

00:22:39.187 --> 00:22:40.886
oyf SHETOPSHISKE

00:22:40.993 --> 00:22:44.632
iz gevezn dort a tsenter fun mener UNK.

00:22:45.397 --> 00:22:48.210
un ayer man hot oykh gearbet als tsushnayder?

00:22:48.468 --> 00:22:53.441
mayn man ot, iz geven a tsushnayder, ober er hot gearbet in a gesheft,

00:22:54.138 --> 00:22:56.253
iz er geven nisht nor tsushnayder

00:22:56.253 --> 00:22:58.355
nor mester un tsukloyber,

00:22:58.355 --> 00:23:00.107
a far⟨UNK⟩ mentsh.

00:23:00.112 --> 00:23:02.688
un er hot gehat a gute parnose?

00:23:02.036 --> 00:23:04.016
er hot gehat a gute parnose.

00:23:04.016 --> 00:23:06.098
er hot zeyer gut, er hot zeyer gut fardint.

00:23:05.883 --> 00:23:08.780
un ets hot tsuzamen oykh gevoynt in Varshe?

00:23:08.752 --> 00:23:10.327
ver ver?

00:23:10.338 --> 00:23:13.269
mir? in Varshe, yo. oyf SHENSHLIVE elef.

00:23:13.950 --> 00:23:17.741
ir hot oykh nokh vay- yo. ir hot oykh nokh vayter gearbet?

00:23:14.017 --> 00:23:15.716
mir hobn khasene gehat,

00:23:18.658 --> 00:23:21.538
ikh hob nokh gearbet biz ikh hob gehat dos kind.

00:23:21.763 --> 00:23:23.799
ven iz dos kind geboyrn?

00:23:23.197 --> 00:23:26.853
dos kind iz geboyrn in akht un draysikstn yor?

00:23:27.062 --> 00:23:29.995
vi azoy, se a yingl, a meydl?

00:23:28.952 --> 00:23:30.144
a meydele.

00:23:29.995 --> 00:23:31.849
vi azoy heyst zi?

00:23:31.500 --> 00:23:32.473
Sara.

00:23:35.615 --> 00:23:40.388
ir hot gefilt antisemitizm? ir hot gevust vos tut zikh in Daytshland?

00:23:40.258 --> 00:23:42.362
mir hobn zeyer fil gevust.

00:23:42.519 --> 00:23:47.678
vayl se hot zi-, in di firme vu se hot zikh ongetun UNK,

00:23:48.560 --> 00:23:53.246
zogt azoy vi UNK, lomir shraybn azoy vi ikh zog, vayl oyf yidish kumt es oys,

00:23:53.370 --> 00:23:54.883
der MERKAZ

00:23:55.007 --> 00:23:57.431
fun ontun zikh Sheyn.

00:23:57.251 --> 00:24:02.100
dos iz di firme vu ayer man hot gearbet? vi azoy hot es geheysn oyf poylish?

00:23:58.584 --> 00:23:59.518
yo.

00:23:59.518 --> 00:24:01.548
Khmelnye zibn un tsvontsik.

00:24:02.364 --> 00:24:05.565
oyf poylish heyst es UNK.

00:24:06.026 --> 00:24:08.957
ober dos iz geven Khmelnye zibn un tsvontsik.

00:24:08.726 --> 00:24:10.104
in Varshe.

00:24:09.502 --> 00:24:11.589
in Varshe, in poylishn gegnt.

00:24:11.240 --> 00:24:12.247
yo.

00:24:12.708 --> 00:24:18.097
un un mir hobn gehat a radyo azoy vi me hot zikh nor, azoy vi me hot nor khasene gehat.

00:24:18.142 --> 00:24:19.852
keyn televizye iz dokh nisht geven.

00:24:19.852 --> 00:24:22.642
nor radyos ho'mir gehat ale mol di nayste.

00:24:22.833 --> 00:24:25.066
vayl der direktor fun Filipsen

00:24:25.066 --> 00:24:27.252
hot zikh ongetun bay mayn man,

00:24:27.272 --> 00:24:30.256
un er hot, un alemen oysergeveyntlekh, ale shoes,

00:24:30.256 --> 00:24:32.160
goyim vos hobn zikh ongetun,

00:24:32.418 --> 00:24:33.732
ale

00:24:33.768 --> 00:24:36.715
PKIDIM, poylishe, zenen geven zeyer elegant,

00:24:36.806 --> 00:24:40.294
un gehandlt alts bay yidn, yidn hobn gegebn oystsutsoln.

00:24:40.670 --> 00:24:43.449
oyf etlekhe mol tsu batsoln yedn khoydesh.

00:24:43.978 --> 00:24:46.085
iz zenen zey ale geven

00:24:46.085 --> 00:24:49.814
ale a khuts der Filips, der f- der fun Filipsen,

00:24:49.814 --> 00:24:54.738
ze- zenen zey geven oysgezen mer vi yidn, mayn man hot oysgezen dafke vi a goy.

00:24:55.706 --> 00:24:57.692
ir vet dokh zen er zet oys vi a goy.

00:24:59.334 --> 00:25:02.686
iz ets hots gehat a radyo, ets hots gehert oyfn,

00:25:01.730 --> 00:25:05.938
gehat keseyder radyo, azoy vi se oyfgekumen epes a frishe zakh

00:25:05.938 --> 00:25:07.499
hobn mir gehat fun dem

00:25:07.499 --> 00:25:09.538
fun dem klyent.

00:25:10.455 --> 00:25:14.094
un durkhn radyo hot ets gevust vos tut zikh in Doytshland?

00:25:12.041 --> 00:25:15.489
me hot alts gevust. in dray un draysikstn yor

00:25:15.489 --> 00:25:19.461
un ale khaveyrim shoyn gevezn demolts trotskyistn,

00:25:19.517 --> 00:25:24.490
un hot men bay mir gehert alts vos tut zikh in in in Berlin.

00:25:25.642 --> 00:25:28.623
di Raykhstag, di opshtimungen, un alding.

00:25:25.902 --> 00:25:26.499
ets hot,

00:25:28.865 --> 00:25:30.214
un ir hot ge,

00:25:29.439 --> 00:25:33.298
me iz geve- ikh mir frier farinteresirt mit politik.

00:25:33.489 --> 00:25:35.643
un hot geven politish aktiv.

00:25:35.970 --> 00:25:38.428
fun di ershte, fun zint tsum seykhl gekumen.

00:25:38.197 --> 00:25:42.815
ayer man iz oykh nokh geven politish aktiv nokh dem vos ets hot khasene gehat?

00:25:42.416 --> 00:25:43.372
yo.

00:25:43.817 --> 00:25:47.760
z- a trotskyist zenen zey gevorn. s'iz geforn avek eyner

00:25:47.934 --> 00:25:51.003
vos a firer fun di trotskyistn,

00:25:51.003 --> 00:25:56.130
ober er iz nisht geven keyn trotskyist un er iz avekgeforn keyn Moskve, avekgeshikt umlegal,

00:25:56.304 --> 00:26:05.389
in der in militerishn akademye oyf a kurs. me hot azoy adurkh, di komunistishe partey hot azoy adurkhgeshmuglt keyn Rusland aktivistn.

00:26:05.400 --> 00:26:07.723
iz er gekumen tsurik a trotskyist.

00:26:07.897 --> 00:26:10.552
er hot gezen vos tut zikh, vos far a lebn s'iz,

00:26:10.552 --> 00:26:12.533
in Moskve un iberal,

00:26:12.723 --> 00:26:15.235
iz er tsurikgekumen, se geshafn gevorn

00:26:15.255 --> 00:26:20.142
a groyse grupe mit aktivistn, afile mit inteligentn,

00:26:21.200 --> 00:26:23.824
vos ikh darf nokh oysrekhenen:

00:26:23.824 --> 00:26:34.756
Aleksander v- vi azoy hot er ge- der der redaktor fun UNK, fun a tsienistishe tsaytung, inteligentn alts.

00:26:34.880 --> 00:26:36.501
un zey hobn gehat a grupe.

00:26:35.184 --> 00:26:39.999
zenen geven onfirer. se geven, neyn, zey zenen geven di di

00:26:39.999 --> 00:26:42.429
teoretiker fun dem trotskyism.

00:26:42.429 --> 00:26:44.527
un se gevezn grupn.

00:26:44.600 --> 00:26:48.723
zenen nisht geven azoy groys vi der komunistisher partey, ober se geven a groy-

00:26:48.723 --> 00:26:52.323
vayl zenen geshtanen shoyn in di shpeterdike y- yorn.

00:26:52.599 --> 00:26:54.652
ober s'iz gevezn.

00:26:56.210 --> 00:26:58.452
un mir hobn zikh a por trotskyistn

00:26:56.385 --> 00:26:57.779
un ir zent oykh geven,

00:26:58.452 --> 00:27:01.604
hobn mir zikh ba- ge- gehaltn tsuzamen.

00:27:02.066 --> 00:27:04.845
ir zent oykh geven politish aktiv?

00:27:04.395 --> 00:27:05.261
ven,

00:27:05.261 --> 00:27:07.579
ven ikh hob gehat dos kind shoyn nisht.

00:27:07.246 --> 00:27:08.115
shoyn nisht.

00:27:07.719 --> 00:27:09.637
ikh hob nisht gearbet oykhet.

00:27:09.896 --> 00:27:13.907
un a kultureln lebn hobn, iz gevezn,

00:27:13.592 --> 00:27:16.778
me hot geleyent a sakh un me hot diskusirt a sakh,

00:27:16.781 --> 00:27:20.634
un dos yor fun nayn un draysikstn yor zenen mir geven

00:27:20.634 --> 00:27:22.429
oyf zumer voynung,

00:27:22.890 --> 00:27:26.310
di gantse khevre, ale hobn kinder, di trotskyistn,

00:27:26.484 --> 00:27:28.503
in nisht vayt fun Varshe.

00:27:29.066 --> 00:27:35.045
azoy noent gevezn az mayn man flegt oyf gearbet Khmelnye zibn un tsvontsik,

00:27:35.090 --> 00:27:38.504
un der vokzal fun hoypt vokzal in Varshe.

00:27:38.504 --> 00:27:42.648
hot zikh ge- iz geven tsuzamen azoy oykhet oyf Khmelnye,

00:27:42.648 --> 00:27:46.715
iz er aroysgeforn oyf der elektrisher ban iz oyfgeshtanen,

00:27:46.715 --> 00:27:50.199
in iz akhtsn minut iz er gevezn in Yedishin,

00:27:50.199 --> 00:27:51.954
oyf Letniske oyf mitog,

00:27:51.954 --> 00:27:53.091
fun gesheft.

00:27:53.349 --> 00:27:54.848
un tsurikgeforn

00:27:54.848 --> 00:27:58.356
un gekumen aheym arum tsurik oyf Letniske,

00:27:59.053 --> 00:28:00.465
zibn a zeyger.

00:28:00.892 --> 00:28:03.299
ven ir zent geven in der zumer voynung.

00:28:02.917 --> 00:28:03.654
yo.

00:28:04.790 --> 00:28:06.978
ir hot gefilt antisemitizm?

00:28:07.372 --> 00:28:08.463
oyf,

00:28:08.216 --> 00:28:09.695
perzenlekh?

00:28:09.617 --> 00:28:10.489
neyn.

00:28:11.253 --> 00:28:16.630
ikh ho- ikh bin nisht ikh bin nisht, ikh hob, ikh bin nisht geven keyn tipishe yidishe UNK.

00:28:11.465 --> 00:28:12.447
ir hot vayl,

00:28:16.721 --> 00:28:18.279
ikh bin geven a blonde,

00:28:18.279 --> 00:28:19.537
mit bloye oygn,

00:28:19.537 --> 00:28:21.289
blonde tsep,

00:28:21.463 --> 00:28:24.692
ober der noz azoy, hob ikh, me hot nisht gezukht demolts.

00:28:24.692 --> 00:28:26.945
me, eynse me hot gevoynt in di yidishn gegnt,

00:28:26.945 --> 00:28:30.553
un in poylishn hot men mikh keyn mol nisht fartshepet.

00:28:32.229 --> 00:28:39.058
heyst ven s'iz oysgebrokhn di krig iz dos eygntlekh geven der ershte, dos ershte mol vos ir hot gefilt antisemitizm?

00:28:39.030 --> 00:28:42.113
se, me hot dos iz es geven.

00:28:42.776 --> 00:28:45.574
un di ale vos zenen geven undzere klyentn

00:28:45.574 --> 00:28:48.916
di patsy- vos mayn man hot mit zey in kontakt,

00:28:48.916 --> 00:28:51.022
zenen gevezn nisht keyn antisemitn.

00:28:52.580 --> 00:28:56.762
un ir hot gevust vos tut zikh in Daytshland oykh mit dem ANTISEMITISMUS?

00:28:54.791 --> 00:28:55.595
me hot a-

00:28:56.799 --> 00:29:00.507
undz ve'mir dos vayter redn oyf di nekste kasete.

00:28:56.984 --> 00:28:58.193
me hot,

00:29:00.427 --> 00:29:01.198
yo.
